graph TB
    Start[FalkorDB data loss detected] --> Qdrant{Qdrant<br/>intact?}
    Qdrant -->|Yes| Connect[Connect to Qdrant API]
    Qdrant -->|No| Backup{Have<br/>backups?}
    
    Connect --> Scan[Scan all points in collection]
    Scan --> Extract[Extract payload metadata]
    Extract --> Validate[Validate required fields]
    
    Validate -->|Valid| Reconstruct[Reconstruct Memory node]
    Validate -->|Missing fields| Skip[Skip memory<br/>log warning]
    
    Reconstruct --> Write[MERGE to FalkorDB]
    Skip --> Count[Increment skip counter]
    Write --> Next{More<br/>memories?}
    Count --> Next
    
    Next -->|Yes| Scan
    Next -->|No| Report[Generate recovery report]
    
    Backup -->|Yes| RestoreBackup[Restore from backup<br/>See Backup Strategies]
    Backup -->|No| DataLoss[Data loss unrecoverable<br/>Start fresh]